         <abstract>
            <p>The threat of unemployment is a paramount challenge to our nation. Totalitarianism and federal public works are not the answer. States and local governments must be permitted to perform the obligations within their sphere. Business must realize that it cannot do the job alone. There is a real fear that taxation may cripple the incentive to invest. Business profits should be taxed only after distribution to the owners as individuals, and personal income taxes must be severely slashed. Business and government must get together to insure permanent and maximum use of our manpower and resources.</p>
